info.description:
The SD-LAN SD-WAN Network View API is a modern REST API based on the OpenAPI specification. The Network View API gives users read rights to retrieve information from the `Network View API` resources. Allowed methods: `GET` --- ## [KPN Developer](https://developer.kpn.com/)
[Getting Started](https://developer.kpn.com/getting-started) ---
